summary: This is a mod that was made for MMOxReview He is epic! This is just a little fun mod.
descriptionHtml:
Hello this is a cool braith fun mod.
Before we get started i would recommend getting KILLABLE CHILDREN MOD as I am not sure if you can kill the braiths without it :P. This mod was made for MMOxReview because he hates braith + I think it is just so fun killing massive braiths for fun! I am a  modder and this is my first ever mod. If you think it sucks then fine :S. 

To get to the braith lair!
---------------------------------
To get to the braith lair you must type in on the console coc braithlair  and to leave type coc riverwood. There is also another lair but it is still in work progress. To get to the work in progress one type coc braithslairofepic and to return type coc riverwood

Added Npcs
------------------
Braith Master
Braith Kill-Kid

thank you and enjoy the mod :D
mod by: philanross
